data.title: St. George Shoots the Dragon
data.meta_description: St. George Shoots the Dragon (2009) starring Lazar Ristovski, Nataa Janji Medani, Borivoje Todorovi and directed by Sran Dragojevi.
data.text: Love triangle story between the village gendarme ore, his wife Katarina and the young disabled war veteran Gavrilo during the time between First Balkan War and World War I.
